# Pokéchess custom starting line-up (BONUS).
# Rename this file to "board_config.csv" to use it instead of the default
# setup. One piece per line:  player;row;col;numPokedex
#   player -> rouge | vert
#   row    -> 0..8   (rows 0-2 are rouge's side, 6-8 are vert's side)
#   col    -> 0..8
#   num    -> Gen 1 pokedex number (1..151).  150 = Mewtwo (the "king").
# Lines starting with '#' and blank lines are ignored. Any cell not listed
# here stays empty, so remember to give EACH player exactly one Mewtwo (150).

# --- A minimal example: just the two kings and a couple of guards ---
rouge;0;4;150
rouge;1;3;6
rouge;1;5;9
vert;8;4;150
vert;7;3;6
vert;7;5;9
